




VNAV: a dip picker's interface
------------------------------

Usage:
	vnav img.tiff     # browse a single-scale borehole image
	vnav img.%d.tiff  # browse a multi-scale image pyramid

Interaction:
	q	exit
	,	save screenshot
	;	save fancy screenshot

Navigation:
	+	decrease octave (zoom out)
	-	increase octave (zoom in)
	1	reset zoom
	arrows	scroll up, down, cycle left, right
	ARROWS	slower scroll
	^arrows	faster scroll
	PgUp	large scroll up
	PgDown	large scroll down

Computation:
	h	compute hough space
	a,s	increase, decrease parameter SIGMA (pre-smothing/window width)
	d,f	increase, decrase parameter ETA (hough smoothing)
	w,e	increase, decrease hough space radius
	z,x	increase, decrase number of random samples
	t	toggle structure tensor
	r	toggle randomized voting
	v	nfa

Display:
	u	toggle hud
	c	toggle autocontrast
	y	toggle inpainting
	o	toggle inferno
	n	normalize contrast
	0	reset cylinder phase

Mouse:
	wheel	increase, decrease octave
	drag	scroll and cycle
	WHEEL	increase, decraease contrast
	middle	print value under cursor
	right	reset zoom and position
	^move	base contrast at the point under cursor
	MOVE	center contrast at the point under cursor
